{"arkId":"cl010096920","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010096920","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre en forme de croix","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre en forme de croix"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1585 - 1600","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1585,"endYear":1600,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Phelizot, C.","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MRR 241","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre cruciforme en cristal de roche bris\u00e9, partiellement remplac\u00e9 par une plaque en argent ; armatures grav\u00e9es de fleurettes et stri\u00e9es. Pendant en forme de chapiteau, bouton moulur\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027oppos\u00e9. Plaque aux bras arrondis, surpportant le cadran, grav\u00e9e de rinceaux, d\u0027une t\u00eate d\u0027angelot et une all\u00e9gorie de la Prudence. Disque horaire couvert d\u0027un \u00e9mail bleu translucide, chiffres romains en r\u00e9serve ; au centre, \u00e9mail translucide rouge. Aiguille ayant la forme de la colombe du Saint-Esprit couverte d\u0027un \u00e9mail blanc opaque o\u00f9 se d\u00e9tachent des motifs en or r\u00e9serv\u00e9. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau, coq \u00e0 un pied ajour\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier. Cliquet d\u00e9pourvu d\u0027ornements, piliers en forme de balustre.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : C Phelizot\/ADijon","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Dijon (Bourgogne-\u003EC\u00f4te-d\u0027Or = C\u00f4te d\u0027Or)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Pierre R\u00e9voil (1776-1842), achat en 1828.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"R\u00e9voil, Pierre","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1828","startYear":1828,"endYear":1828}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"place":[{"value":"Dijon"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 39","